st lawrenc seaway open still march 31 the st lawrenc seaway between lake ontario and montreal is still schedul to open for the ship season on march 31 , a seaway offici said . the great lake could have been open for traffic earlier thi month due to the mild winter , but schedul repair to the welland canal join lake eri with lake ontario will keep that section close until the april 1 open , she said . one lock system in the four-lock soo canal join lake superior with huron wa open on the morn of march 22 , but onli three commerci vessel have been lock through so far , accord to an u.s. armi corp of engin offici . the soo canal is current onli open for daylight vessel movement , with 24 hour movement allow begin march 29 , she ad .